Planning<\/strong>: We outline what content is needed, where it belongs, and how it supports your messaging and SEO goals.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1474\" data-end=\"1573\">This stage ensures your website isn\u2019t just attractive\u2014it works exactly how your users expect it to.<\/p>\n<hr class=\"\" data-start=\"1575\" data-end=\"1578\" \/>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"1580\" data-end=\"1607\">3. Design &amp; Development<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1609\" data-end=\"1741\">We translate the wireframes and strategy into a modern, responsive website that reflects your brand and performs across all devices.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1743\" data-end=\"2081\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1743\" data-end=\"1846\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1745\" data-end=\"1846\"><strong data-start=\"1745\" data-end=\"1768\">Full Visual Mockups<\/strong>: We design key pages and present them for feedback before development starts.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1847\" data-end=\"1943\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1849\" data-end=\"1943\"><strong data-start=\"1849\" data-end=\"1867\">Feedback Loops<\/strong>: Your team is involved at every milestone so you\u2019re never left in the dark.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"1944\" data-end=\"2081\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1946\" data-end=\"2081\"><strong data-start=\"1946\" data-end=\"1972\">Mobile-First Execution<\/strong>: Design and code prioritise mobile usability, given that most Kenyan traffic originates from mobile devices.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2083\" data-end=\"2205\">Our developers then code the site using clean, scalable, standards-compliant HTML\/CSS\/JS, integrated with your chosen CMS.<\/p>\n<hr class=\"\" data-start=\"2207\" data-end=\"2210\" \/>\n<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"2212\" data-end=\"2235\">4. Testing &amp; Launch<\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2237\" data-end=\"2314\">We don\u2019t launch until everything works as it should\u2014fo